just nod my head and say, “Mmmm?” Or
should I follow my gut reaction and shout,
“By the beard of Beelzebub, how is that
POSSIBLE???”

After all, Stir‘ Wars isn’t just a popular
science—ﬁction movie. It’s not even just a ﬁlm
